projects.name: Food Delivery Website
projects.description: Developed using the MERN stack enabling seamless integration between front-end and back-end components resulting in a significant improvement in development efficiency. Established secure user authentication and authorization mechanisms with JWT and bcrypt, ensuring robust protection for user data and secure access control reducing unauthorized access attempts. Implemented a shopping cart system, allowing users to add, remove, and update items, and checkout process integrating with payment gateways with Stripe for secure transactions.

projects.name: PersonaLearn - LMS
projects.description: Engineered PersonaLearn using HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and Tailwind CSS for a responsive front-end, enhancing user engagement and interaction. Integrated advanced Machine Learning and NLP algorithms to personalize course recommendations, increasing course completion rates. Utilized Python, PHP, and MySQL for the back-end, ensuring robust data management and reliable system performance, improving data retrieval efficiency.

projects.name: Disease Prediction Using Deep Learning
projects.description: Implemented deep learning models including ResNet50, MobileNet, and InceptionV3, achieving an average prediction accuracy of 85%. Conducted extensive experiments with hyperparameters (learning rates, batch sizes) and optimizers (Adam, SGD), resulting in a significant improvement in model performance compared to baseline configurations. Utilized TensorFlow and scikit-learn libraries to develop disease prediction systems, achieving a notable increase in diagnostic accuracy and optimizing treatment planning efficacy.

experiences.description: Applied advanced ML algorithms on datasets exceeding 100,000 entries, resulting in a significant increase in decision-making accuracy and a reduction in error rates, thereby enhancing predictive precision. Employed five diverse machine learning methods to significantly boost operational efficiency, reducing processing time and cutting costs.
